reviewText: Said that it had spanish subtitles, didn't have them.

Seller: "1stVideo"  will NOT give SHIPPING INFO -Nor- TRACKING INFO..  Even though the ITEM  SHIPPED 6 DAYS AGO ! ..on January 8, 2014.  Wondering what is going on with many Amazon Sellers?  As an extremely good customer of Amazon doing much of our primary yearly shopping on AMazon for over ten years, as of the past 1 year we have had nothing but problems with MANY AMAZON SELLERS.  ISSUES, such as: Not providing us with Tracking Info after our PURCHASE has been completed and money taken, Shipping boxes without any packing filler to protect purchased merchandise and merchandise crushed and packaging badly ripped apart, Items smelling of strange odors such as napkins and candles, Sellers doubling the amount of items purchased, such as 2 dvds of the same program, and 3 cds of the same musical program and many more problems.  This has happened at least 30 times in the past one year !!
